The paper discusses the dynamics of gradient descent in deep nonlinear networks and its relationship to the generalization properties of the network. This topic is most closely related to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG), as well as neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and information theory (cs.IT).
